<HEAD>UNDATED: Western Europe.</HEAD>
<TEXT>
 DEC. 20 _ <ORGANIZATION> PLO </ORGANIZATION> mutiny forces evacuation of leader <PERSON> Yasser </PERSON> <PERSON> Arafat </PERSON> and 4,000 followers from last stronghold in <LOCATION> Lebanon </LOCATION>.
</TEXT>
<NOTE>1984</NOTE>
<NOTE>MORNING IN AMERICA</NOTE>
