<HEAD>For Release Weekend Editions Dec. 16-17 and Thereafter</HEAD>
<HEAD>The Fascinating and the Not-So: Another Decade-Full of Trivia</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: Leads b0799 of Dec. 7. Expands lead graf; SUBS 8th graf, `3.
Winky, Blinky ..., to CORRECT Winky to Inky; SUBS 40th graf, `15. In the
..., to restore dropped matter; SUBS 47th graf, `The native ..., to CORRECT
spelling of Trebek, sted Trebeck.</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By SCOTT WILLIAMS</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
