nt months. <PERSON> Konney </PERSON> declined to comment on whether the restructuring program came in response to a takeover threat. Through three quarters of this year, <ORGANIZATION> Tambrands </ORGANIZATION> earned $ 61 million, or $ 2.72 a share, down from $ 71 million, or $ 3.17 a share, a year earlier. Nine-month revenue totaled $ 449 million this year, up from $ 428 million in 1988.
